    "title": "Rethe DJ set",
    "description": "Rethe is a versatile DJ, producer, and live performer known for his hypnotic grooves that blend lo-fi and hi-fi sounds. Co-founder of the music collective Calosc, Rethe has been captivating audiences since 2016 with his unique style and innovative approach to electronic music. His tracks and releases are available on platforms like Beatport and SoundCloud, where he continues to push the boundaries of his craft"
  },
  {
    "url": "https://www.donaldjtrump.com",
    "title": "Mini PEACE",
    "description": "The Mini PEACE Festival is an annual event held in Trondheim, Norway that celebrates the ideals of peace, freedom, and women's rights through music, art, and dialogue. The festival features concerts, exhibitions, workshops, and other cultural programs that highlight the perspectives and experiences of women in conflict zones and peace-building efforts."
